Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:43.85,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,D-Did he go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.07,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:50.60,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,I’m Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.85,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Um... Please give me an invitation \N to one of the Champion’s matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.35,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Dande’s matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.60,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,Why w-would you ask m-me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:07.46,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,I just thought a Gym Leader \N might be able to get one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:09.85,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.49,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,It’s not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:16.35,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,It’s for my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.87,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:28.27,Main,John,0,0,0,,I wonder if someday I’ll get to \N be a Pokémon Trainer and go on a journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.46,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,A Pokémon Trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:32.85,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,There’s no way, \N and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.60,Main,John,0,0,0,,Well then, \N what do {\i1}you{\i0} want to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:38.60,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,We don’t...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:42.33,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,...even know when we’ll get \N discharged from this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:46.81,Main,John,0,0,0,,But Chairman Rose said \N I’d make a great trainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.93,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,But he still hasn’t {\i1}replied{\i0} \N to your letter, has he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:53.18,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Stop holding on to \N impossible dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.69,Main,John,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.54,Main,John,0,0,0,,Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.18,Main,John,0,0,0,,Don’t hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.18,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Because it’s just not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:22.18,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Then I got discharged by myself \N before I could apologize. {Added linebreak. Also, suggesting "by myself" in place of "on my own" and "could" in place of "got the chance to". - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.79,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,John really loves Dande.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:30.22,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,I thought I could make it up to him by \N giving him a ticket to one of Dande’s matches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.80,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:48.93,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.43,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,I-If you want to make up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:57.59,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,T-Then you should just talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.22,Main,Onion,0,0,0,,T-To the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.31,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.71,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.56,Main,John,0,0,0,,Tommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.31,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,It went all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.33,Main,John,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.06,Main,John,0,0,0,,They said they’d keep an eye \N on my recovery for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.64,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.43,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,John.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.81,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.06,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,I take back what I said last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.81,Main,John,0,0,0,,Tommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:42.64,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,When you’re {\i1}really{\i0} into something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.14,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,you lose sight of everything around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.53,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,and put yourself in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.44,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,But once you make up your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.27,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,you never, ever back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.89,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,So I’m sure you’ll become \N a great Pokémon Trainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:02.11,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,As soon as you get discharged...\N I’ll help you out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:06.64,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Let’s become the best trainers, \N together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.14,Main,John,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:42.88,Main,Tommy,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:02.49,Main,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,They sure are taking their time... \N Are those kids okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:14.18,Main,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,Sir, why did you want to go \N to the hospital so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.97,Main,Dande,0,0,0,,Does my face really look like this?
